/*
name
symbol
Risk Factor
# of Collateral
Past & Current Loans:
Loan Amount
Amount Remaining
Interest Rate
Payment Details
Time Period on Payments
Type of currency
USD Value
Total number of payments/loans
Total Interest

Any failed loans

pragma solidity >=0.6.0 <0.8.0;

contract NFTLoan {
    string public name = "NFTLoan";
    string public symbol = "NFTLOAN";
}
